quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,Kiya aap ney unn ki taraf nazar nahi daali jinhon ney Allah ki nemat kay badley na shukri ki aur apni qom ko halakat kay ghar mein laa utara
  14,29,Yani dozakh mein jiss mien yeh sab jayen gay jo bad tareen thikana hai
  14,30,Enhon ney Allah kay humsar bana liye kay logon ko Allah ki raah say behkayen. Aap keh dijiye kay khair mazay kerlo tumhari baaz gasht to aakhir jahannum hi hai
  14,31,Meray eman walay bandon say keh dijiye kay namazon ko qaeem rakhen aur jo kuch hum ney dey rakha hai uss mein say kuch na kuch posheeda aur zahir kharach kertay rahen iss say pehlay kay woh din aajaye jiss mein na kharid-o-farokht hogi na dosti aur mohabbat
  14,32,Allah woh hai jiss ney aasmanon aur zamin ko peda kiya hai aur aasmanon say barish barsa ker iss kay zariye say tumhari rozi kay liye phal nikaley hain aur kashtiyon ko tumharay bus mein ker diya hai kay daryaon mein uss kay hukum say chalen phiren. Ussi ney nadiyan aur nehren tumharay ikhtiyar mein ker di hain
  14,33,Ussi ney tumharay liye sooraj chand ko musakhar kerdiya hai kay barabar hi chal rahey hain aur raat din ko bhi tumharay kaam mein laga rakha hai
  14,34,Ussi ney tumhen tumhari mun mangi kul cheezon mein say dey rakha hai. Agar tum Allah kay ehsan ginna chahao to unhen pooray ginn bhi nahi saktay. Yaqeenan insan bara hi bey insaf aur na shukra hai
  14,35,(Ibrahim ki yeh dua bhi yaad kero) jab unhon ney kaha kay aey meray perwerdigar! Iss shehar ko aman wala bana dey aur mujhay aur meri aulad ko butt parasti say panah dey
  14,36,Aey meray paalney walay mabood! Enhon ney boht say logon ko raah say bhatka diya hai. Pus meri tabeydaari kerney wala mera hai aur jo meri na farmani keray to tu boht hi moaf aur karam kerney wala hai
  14,37,Aey humaray perwerdigar! Mein ney apni kuch aulad iss bey kheti ki wadi mein teray hurmat walay ghar kay pass basaee hai. Aey humaray perwerdigar! Yeh iss liye kay woh namaz qaeem rakhen pus to kuch logon kay dilon ko inn ki taraf maeel ker dey. Aur enhen phalon ki roiziyan inayat farma takay yeh shukar guzari keren
  14,38,Aey humaray perwerdigar! Tu khoob janta hai jo hum chupayen aur jo zahir keren. Zamin-o-aasman ki koi cheez Allah per posheeda nahi
  14,39,Allah ka shukar hai jiss ney mujhay iss burhapay mein ismail (alh-e-salam) aur ishaq (alh-e-salam) ata farmaye. Kuch shak nahi kay mera palanhaar Allah duaon ka sunnay wala hai
  14,40,Aey meray paalney walay! Mujhay namaz ka paband rakh aur meri aulad say bhi aey humaray rab meri dua qabool farma
  14,41,Aey humaray perwerdigar! Mujhay bakhsh dey aur meray maa baap ko bhi bakhsh aur digar momino ko bhi bakhsh jiss din hisab honey lagay
  14,42,Na insafon kay aemaal say Allah ko ghafil na samajh woh to enhen uss din tak mohlat diye huye hai jiss din aankhen phati ki phati reh jayen gi
  14,43,Woh apney sir upper uthaye dor bhaag ker rahey hongay khud apni taraf bhi inn ki nighayen na loten gi aur inn kay dil khali aur array huye hongay
  14,44,Logon ko uss din say hoshiyaar ker dey jab kay unn kay pass azab aajaye ga aur zalim kahen gay aey humaray rab humen boht thoray qarib kay waqt tak ki hi mohlat dey kay hum teri tableegh maan len aur teray payghumbaron ki tabeydaari mein lagg jayen. Kiya tum iss say pehlay bhi qasmen nahi kha rahey thay? Kay tumharay liye duniya say talna hi nahi
  14,45,Aur kiya tum inn logon kay gharon mein rehtay sehtay na thay jinhon ney apni jano per zulm kiya aur kiya tum per woh moamla khula nahi kay hum ney unn kay sath kaisa kuch kiya. Hum ney (to tumharay samjhaney ko) boht si misalen biyan ker di thin
  14,46,Yeh apni apni chalen chal rahey hain aur Allah ko inn ki tamam chalon ka ilm hai aur inn ki chalen aisi na thin kay unn say pahar apni jagah say tal jayen
  14,47,Aap hergiz yeh khayal na keren kay Allah apney nabiyon say wada khilafi keray ga Allah bara hi ghalib aur badla lenay wala hai
  14,48,Jiss din zamin iss zamin kay siwa aur hi badal dijayegi aur aasman bhi aur sab kay sab Allah wahid ghalbay walay kay roo-baroo hongay
  14,49,Aap uss din gunehgaron ko dekhen gay kay zanjeeron mein milay julay aik jagah jakray huye hongay
  14,50,Unn kay libad gandhak kay hongay aur aag unn kay chehron per bhi charhi hui hogi
  14,51,Yeh iss liye kay Allah Taalaa her shaks ko uss kay kiye huye aemaal ka badla dey be-shak Allah Taalaa ko hisab letay kuch dair nahi lagney ki
  14,52,Yeh quran tamam logon kay liye itlaa naama hai kay iss kay zariye say woh hoshiyaar ker diye jayen aur bakhoobhi maloom kerlen kay Allah aik hi mabood hai aur takay aqal mand log soch samajh len